title: Carb Smart Creamy Chicken Breasts and Bacon-Cauliflower Chowder with Cheddar Cheese and Chives
description: This creamy chicken chowder gets its depth from nutty-sweet roasted cauliflower and salty bacon fat. Extra crunch from the seeds and bacon bits on top make it an unforgettable bowl of goodness!

